        "code": "/**\n * {@inheritDoc}\n */\n@Override\nprotected void readChild(FreeColXMLReader xr) throws XMLStreamException {\n    final String tag = xr.getLocalName();\n    if (Scope.getXMLElementTagName().equals(tag)) {\n        addScope(new Scope(xr));\n    } else {\n        super.readChild(xr);\n    }\n}"
